# === Inner canopy mass (lighter green, covers the branch bases) ===
circle 1,1 0.45 fill #1a4a12 0.6
circle 1,1 0.45 stroke #0e380a 0.3
circle 0.92,0.92 0.30 fill #1e5a16 0.4
circle 1.08,0.95 0.28 fill #1e5216 0.35
